text: Sheikh Jaber al-Ahmad al-Sabah (born 16 June 1929 in Kuwait City - 15 January 2006) was an Emir of Kuwait, also known as the Last Emir in and before the Iraqi Invasion of Kuwait. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:2006 deaths Category:Deaths from cerebral hemorrhage
title: Jaber Al-Ahmad Al-Sabah
